{"tid":142343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小海豚被活捉驚到嘔 「驟眼睇好似嘔出腸」","createTime":"2017-03-03T16:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T04:52:38.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e699a796592d1ba8e0d90705744dd1673bf09138","tid":142343,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:15:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>小海豚被活捉驚到嘔 「驟眼睇好似嘔出腸」<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170303/56378467\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170303%2F56378467&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2Bv5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=065ca0b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170303%2F56378467&h=0257c5ae\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170303/56378467</a></strong></div></span><br />\n<br />\n網上近日流傳日本太地町海豚被活捉時受驚嘔吐的一幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。片段所見，捕豚者包圍年幼的海豚後，徒手把牠活捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。海豚雖然拼命掙扎，但最終無法脫身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170303/large/1488506132_9c0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170303%2Flarge%2F1488506132_9c0a.jpg&h=70fc0c79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n片段由凱特（Liz Cater）上月拍下。她說：「其中一條海豚在嘔吐，驟眼看以為牠嘔出自己的腸臟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。」她指，被「嚇到嘔」的海豚不只一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n這些海豚被捕捉後，會送往日本、中國、台灣、俄羅斯、杜拜、墨西哥、印尼等地的海洋公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n太地町是紀錄片《血色海灣》的拍攝地。該片敘述每年在太地町屠殺海豚傳統，過程中海水會被染成鮮紅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，引起國際團體撻伐。"},{"pid":"6b31fe9a3b37fb566ec0d6405a2c911ddfe4c10a","tid":142343,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T00:00:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6659b6eff0fef5806eacea66bbe9081b6d42e4e","tid":142343,"uid":9382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T00:12:28.000Z","msg":"真係唔好去動物園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5670d5b9baafe9b5634a7cbc96bc14147461779","tid":142343,"uid":23863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T00:17:31.000Z","msg":"有啲傳統真係好撚嘔心。"},{"pid":"fdfc37bd0b4537668f2569f730beaef326d858f4","tid":142343,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T10:40:58.000Z","msg":"玩老笠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d32b198f45ca83e480109dbd52217085d90a67","tid":142343,"uid":55466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T10:52:09.000Z","msg":"架狗<br />\n好L賤"},{"pid":"dce2e986aa0762261941837204f84d6713ea6ca0","tid":142343,"uid":73613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:20:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5c1022239fa7bdd397ff43df78184c08b233cd4","tid":142343,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:46:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有啲傳統真係好撚嘔心。</blockquote><br />\n傳咩統， 搵錢就搵錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d77a472a824c3bc3a76270edf3565d20a63e1045","